            <p class="hca-typography--body-1">Display a smaller text input field with a magnifying glass icon and the word "Search".  Use no less than 115px width for the field.</p>
            <p class="hca-typography--body-1">Clicking the search input causes the toolbar to transform, clearing other content and expanding the search text field full width. If voice search is supported, the microphone icon also appears.</p>
